#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.drop"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:1 of
msgid "Drop specified labels from rows or columns."
msgstr "从行或列中删除指定的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:3 of
msgid ""
"Remove rows or columns by specifying label names and corresponding axis, "
"or by specifying directly index or column names. When using a multi-"
"index, labels on different levels can be removed by specifying the level."
msgstr ""
"通过指定标签名称和对应的轴，或者直接指定索引或列名称来删除行或列。在使用"
"多级索引时，可以指定级别来删除不同级别的标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:8 of
msgid "Index or column labels to drop."
msgstr "要删除的索引或列标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:10 of
msgid ""
"Whether to drop labels from the index (0 or 'index') or columns (1 or "
"'columns')."
msgstr "是从索引（0 或 'index'）还是列（1 或 'columns'）中删除标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:13 of
msgid ""
"Alternative to specifying axis (``labels, axis=0`` is equivalent to "
"``index=labels``)."
msgstr "指定轴的替代方式（``labels, axis=0`` 等价于 ``index=labels``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:16 of
msgid ""
"Alternative to specifying axis (``labels, axis=1`` is equivalent to "
"``columns=labels``)."
msgstr "指定轴的替代方式（``labels, axis=1`` 等价于 ``columns=labels``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:19 of
msgid "For MultiIndex, level from which the labels will be removed."
msgstr "对于 MultiIndex，指定要从中删除标签的级别。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:21 of
msgid "If True, do operation inplace and return None."
msgstr "如果为 True，则就地操作并返回 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:23 of
msgid ""
"If 'ignore', suppress error and only existing labels are dropped. Note "
"that errors for missing indices will not raise."
msgstr ""
"如果为 'ignore'，则忽略错误，仅删除存在的标签。注意，缺失索引的错误不会"
"引发异常。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:27 of
msgid "DataFrame without the removed index or column labels."
msgstr "删除了指定索引或列标签的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:30 of
msgid "If any of the labels is not found in the selected axis."
msgstr "如果在所选轴中找不到任何标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:35 of
msgid "Label-location based indexer for selection by label."
msgstr "基于标签位置的索引器，用于按标签选择。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.dropna`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:38 of
msgid ""
"Return DataFrame with labels on given axis omitted where (all or any) "
"data are missing."
msgstr "返回在给定轴上省略了标签的 DataFrame，其中（全部或部分）数据缺失。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.drop_duplicates`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:41 of
msgid ""
"Return DataFrame with duplicate rows removed, optionally only considering"
" certain columns."
msgstr "返回删除了重复行的 DataFrame，可选择仅考虑某些列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.drop`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:44 of
msgid "Return Series with specified index labels removed."
msgstr "返回删除了指定索引标签的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:47 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:59 of
msgid "Drop columns"
msgstr "删除列"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:73 of
msgid "Drop a row by index"
msgstr "通过索引删除行"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.drop.df_drop:79 of
msgid "Drop columns and/or rows of MultiIndex DataFrame"
msgstr "删除 MultiIndex DataFrame 的列和/或行"

